additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
Welcome to the Wizard Bridge Telegram community! Our aim is to connect various blockchain networks. Join our community to stay updated on our latest developments, partnerships, and events. Let's build a better future for decentralized finance together.
We are excited to have you on board as we continue to build and expand our multichain bridge. Here are some important links that you may find useful:

1. Website: https://wizardbridge.com
2. Telegram Group: https://t.me/wizardbridge
3. Twitter: https://twitter.com/wizardbridge_
4. Wiz Staking DApp: https://arbwizard.com
5. Sushiswap: https://app.sushi.com/swap?chainId=42161&inputCurrency=ETH&outputCurrency=0x2404572eaA937c5A64C84Ee597fAAe4C13823782
6. Whitepaper: coming soon…

Please make sure to follow us on our social media platforms for the latest updates and developments on Wizard Bridge. Don't hesitate to reach out to us in the Telegram group for any questions or concerns. We're here to help!
